{"article_id":"cmgpl7kHkIXfHYox","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Seattle was the first big city","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to pass a $ 15 minimum wage .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"it 's pretty awesome","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"since I benefit from it , ''","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"one told us .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Another added :","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"`` I wish","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"it was all over the place , not just Seattle . ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Now , five years after the law passed ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"the evidence is in :","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"While some workers did earn more ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"entry-levels jobs decreased .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The politicians never mentioned that","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"when they passed the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"says Erin Shannon of the Washington Policy Center :","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` It 's really presented by minimum wage advocates as...a win-win for employers...a win-win for workers . ''","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"She pointed us to a factory","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that moved hundreds of jobs out of state ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and to a store","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that stopped hiring beginners","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"because of the $ 15 minimum wage .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"`` The politicians , in Seattle especially , have no sense whatsoever about what it means to small businesses like us , ''","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"the owner of Retrofit Home tells us .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"A minimum wage hurts young people","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"who need a first job ,","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"say three young people","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"who won a contest","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"organized by Stossel in The Classroom ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"which provides free videos and lesson plans about free markets to teachers .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Dillon Hodes won the high-school-level video contest .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"He says","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"a friend","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"who worked at Kroger","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"saw her hours cut","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"as the store implemented a $ 12 minimum .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"`` Raising the minimum wage causes increased unemployment , ''","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"explains Rigel Noble-Koza , the college-level contest winner .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Stossel says","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"he learned things from Noble-Koza 's video ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"which noted","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that Iceland , Norway , Sweden , and Switzerland have no national minimum wage .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"The minimum wage `` stops us from actually getting a job , ''","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"says Esther Rhoads ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"who won the high school essay contest .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"She points out","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that the earliest advocates of the minimum-wage wanted to price black Americans out of the market .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"About 100 years ago , blacks were often paid less","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"but they were more likely to be employed than whites .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Rep . Miles Clayton Allgood","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"( D-Ala . )","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he hoped","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"the minimum wage would stop `` cheap colored labor in competition with white labor . ''","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` It was meant...to keep the poor and the minorities from getting jobs , ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Esther tells Stossel .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Esther explains :","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` I 'm 14 .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"It 'd be very difficult for me to find a job-my labor would n't be worth $ 15 an hour . ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"`` If only politicians were as smart as those kids , ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Stossel says .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The views","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"expressed in this video","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"are solely those of ; his independent production company , Stossel Productions ; and the people","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"he interviews .","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"The claims and opinions","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"set forth in the video and accompanying text","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"are not necessarily those of Reason .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":135,"left":128,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":91,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":76,"right":90,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":69,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":72,"right":74,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":2,"right":70,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":6,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":90,"left":79,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":9,"right":78,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":10,"right":77,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":87,"right":88,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":87,"left":81,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":80,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":13,"right":14,"